667
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:21,100
You are too picky, honey.

668
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:23,200
Maybe you're not picky enough.

669
00:28:32,300 --> 00:28:34,200
I just thought
she missed her father.

670
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:37,300
She was trying
not to hurt your feelings.

671
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:39,000
It's all my fault.

672
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:42,900
That bastard!

673
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:46,200
