that night.

674
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,700
- You answered the phone.
- So?

675
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:49,100
Missy wanted a ride home.

676
00:28:49,100 --> 00:28:51,600
Which you never told her mother
or the cops back then?

677
00:28:51,600 --> 00:28:54,000
